transcript:
Customer: Ji sir.
Executive: Ji chal raha hai, madam, koi problem nahi hai.
Customer: Ji chal raha hai, abhi aap system pe ho kya?
Executive: System pe nahi hu, mai phone pe hu abhi.
Executive: Phone pe ho aap, ek minute aapko na video meeting ka link share kar rahi hu, aap isko join kijiyega.
Customer: Dijiye.
Executive: Ek second ha.
Executive: Aapko na whatsapp pe mai share kar rahi hu na.
Customer: Dijiye.
Customer: Ha sir.
Customer: Agar hai theek hai, agar nahi parwah link ke through nahi to share kar paunga yaha se bhi.
Customer: Pehle khol ke.
Executive: Sir ek minute aapke paas to maine whatsapp pe na message kiya hai, mila aapko?
Customer: Sir ab ek baar aapna whatsapp open kijiyega, ja rahe hai.
Customer: Ha ji aa gaya.
Executive: Join kijiyega.
Customer: Ek minute whatsapp pe.
Customer: Kya likha hai open?
Customer: Join video call.
(silence)
(caller tune)
(caller tune)
(caller tune)
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer unable to share through link.



Resolution:

- Executive shared a video meeting link on WhatsApp.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral
